WestLB to Sell Real-Estate Unit This Year, FT Deutschland Says

-- B y   R i c h a r d   W e i s s
-- 
2011-08-26T05:19:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-26/westlb-to-sell-real-estate-unit-this-year-ft-deutschland-says.html
WestLB AG is in advanced talks to
sell Westdeutsche ImmobilienBank AG, its real-estate subsidiary,
to financial investor Apollo Global Management, the  Financial
Times Deutschland  reported, citing comments made by Chief
Executive Officer Dietrich Voigtlaender at a press conference
yesterday.  The transaction should happen this year; for all other
assets to be sold, bidding procedures are in place and dates
have been set, the newspaper cited Voigtlaender as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Richard Weiss  in  Frankfurt  at 
 rweiss5@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at   bkammel@bloomberg.net . 